narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A good course, but depends on your professor!
If you placed into L4 and are just looking to knock off the language requirement, be enthusiastic about the class, have interest or you will end up being bored and unmotivated all semester.
Lots f work but interesting course content
It's a good class with a broad range of material. However be careful in choosing the professor because that's what makes or breaks the class.
This class is demanding but worth taking. I would recommend it to the student with a profound interest in French and French culture.
